reviewText: The product consists of 2 discs with Naina on a single disc and the other side films on a two sided disc. "Night Feeders" is the only film worth watching with a current IMDB rating of 4.8. This triple film feature generally sells cheaper than any of of the single films. There  are no extras. If simply watching just one of the movies is all you want to do, this would be be the way to go.
